OL,3,C'It was inhumane': Daughter slams
OL,4,Cprison after mum neglected and left to
OL,5,Csuffer
OL,7,FAnna Youssef reports from the inquest
OL,8,Fat Cheshire Coroner's Court
OL,10,FA daughter has slammed a prison which
OL,11,F'neglected' her mum and left her to
OL,12,Fsuffer 'inhumanly' before she took her
OL,13,Fown life just two days into a jail
OL,14,Fsentence.
OL,16,FChristine McDonald, 55, was discovered
OL,17,Fby prison officers in her cell at HMP
OL,18,FStyal in with self-inflicted injuries
OL,19,Fon 2 March 2019.
