OL,3,C'It was inhumane': Daughter slams
OL,4,Cprison after mum neglected and left to
OL,5,Csuffer
OL,7,FThe mum-of-four, who struggled with
OL,8,Faddiction, was just days into a 12-
OL,9,Fweek sentence for shoplifting.
OL,11,FHer mental health has deteriorated
OL,12,Fafter she had witnessed her daughter
OL,13,Ffall from the roof of a building just
OL,14,Fhours before she was jailed.
OL,16,FChristine, her inquest was told,
OL,17,Frepeatedly asked prison staff for an
OL,18,Fupdate on her daughter's condition,
OL,19,Fbut got no answer.
