OL,7,FHer situation was compounded by
OL,8,Fserious drug withdrawals, but she was
OL,9,Fnot given methadone treatment to help,
OL,10,Fthe inquest in Warrington also heard.
OL,12,FAfter an inquest jury found her death
OL,13,Fhad been contributed to by neglect,
OL,14,FChristine's youngest daughter Cheri
OL,15,Fcriticised HMP Styal.
OL,17,FCheri McDonald said: "It was horrific
OL,18,Fhow she was treated, how she was
OL,19,Fneglected, how she as calling out for
OL,20,Fhelp and nobody came.
