OL,7,F"She was left to suffer, it was
OL,8,Finhumane, all of it was inhumane."
OL,10,FThe charity Inquest claims Christine
OL,11,Fwas the 11th prisoner to die of self-
OL,12,Finflicted wounds since 2007.
OL,14,FIt also says the prison has had more
OL,15,Finmate deaths than any other in
OL,16,FEngland and Wales.
