OL,7,FThe failure to pass on the message
OL,8,Fabout her daughter also contributed,
OL,9,Fthey said.
OL,11,F"My mum died because she was
OL,12,Fneglected," Cheri said. "She was
OL,13,Fbacked into a corner, suffering and
OL,14,Fnot given ay support or any
OL,15,Facknowledgment of that suffering.
OL,17,F"When people are pushed so far the
OL,18,Foptions become limited and she must
OL,19,Fhave felt that was her only option."
