OL,7,FChristine was charged with two counts
OL,8,Fof shoplifting in 2019, and after
OL,9,Ffailing to attend court on 27 February
OL,10,Fwas arrested alongside her daughter
OL,11,FKirsty.
OL,13,FDuring the arrest on 1 March 2019, her
OL,14,Fdaughter Kristy fell from the roof of
OL,15,Fa third floor building suffering
OL,16,Fserious injuries.
