OL,7,FDespite the incident, Christine was
OL,8,Fnot allowed to stay with her daughter,
OL,9,Fand instead she was taken directly to
OL,10,FBlackpool Magistrates Court where she
OL,11,Fwas jailed for 12 weeks for
OL,12,Fshoplifting and failing to appear at
OL,13,Fcourt.
OL,15,FShe had stolen a block of cheese, a
OL,16,Fbottle of shampoo, hair dye and some
OL,17,Fbubble bath.
