OL,7,FThe mum was then transferred to HMP
OL,8,FStyal - not knowing if her daughter
OL,9,Fwas alive or dead, and unable to
OL,10,Fcontact other family members.
OL,12,FHer behaviour was described as
OL,13,Fanxious, suffering from opiate
OL,14,Fwithdrawal symptoms and being
OL,15,Fconcerned for her daughter, the
OL,16,Finquest was told.
