OL,3,C'It was inhumane': Daughter slams
OL,4,Cprison after mum neglected and left to
OL,5,Csuffer
OL,7,FThe court heard how Cheri McDonald -
OL,8,FChristine's youngest daughter - had
OL,9,Fcalled the prison asking them to
OL,10,Freassure Christine Kristy was alive
OL,11,Fand in hospital.
OL,13,FShe said: "I told them my mum would be
OL,14,Ffreaking out and that it was vital
OL,15,Fthey get this message to her"
OL,17,FThat message was never passed on.
