OL,3,C'It was inhumane': Daughter slams
OL,4,Cprison after mum neglected and left to
OL,5,Csuffer
OL,7,FThe inquest jury was told Christine
OL,8,Fwas unable to give a urine sample -
OL,9,Flikely because she was dehydrated -
OL,10,Fwhich meant medics were unable to see
OL,11,Fif there were drugs in her system.
OL,13,FIn turn this mean she was not given
OL,14,Fmethadone, leaving her suffering from
OL,15,Fagonising withdrawal symptoms.
OL,17,FShe also had low mood and continued to
OL,18,Fask about her daughter, the inquest
OL,19,Fheard.
