OL,7,FChristie was taken to Wythenshawe
OL,8,FHospital on 2 March following concerns
OL,9,Fraised during a healthcare assessment
OL,10,Fin the prison.
OL,12,FLater that day, she was returned to
OL,13,FHMP Styal, where officers found her in
OL,14,Fher cell just a few hours later.
OL,16,FAlthough staff were able to find a
OL,17,Fpulse and she was taken to , she later
OL,18,Fdied.
