OL,7,FCheri said: "I am a nurse in the NHS
OL,8,Fand appreciate the immense workload
OL,9,Facross all public sector services,
OL,10,Fhowever I have serious concerns about
OL,11,Fthe level of care my mum received.
OL,12,F"This is both as a patient when
OL,13,Fphysically unwell withdrawing and the
OL,14,Fsteps the prison took to look after
OL,15,Fher given the massive stressing event
OL,16,Fof watching her daughter, my sister,
OL,17,Fsustain serious injuries."
