OL,7,FThe jury listed a number of failings
OL,8,Fwhich they believe were all factors
OL,9,Fleading to Christine taking her own
OL,10,Flife:
OL,12,FFollowing the conclusion, the coroner
OL,13,Fsaid she would be writing a report to
OL,14,Fthe Governor of HMP Styal, as well as
OL,15,Fthe Ministry of Justice as she is
OL,16,Fconcerned the emergency response codes
OL,17,Fat the prison are still not well
OL,18,Funderstood, which could lead to delays
OL,19,Fin medical treatment and further
OL,20,Fdeaths.
