OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,9,Fwith the friends and family of
OL,10,FChristine McDonald.
OL,12,F"We are investing #14m to improve
OL,13,Fsafety in women's prisons and
OL,14,Fstrengthening the support provided to
OL,15,Fthose at risk of self-harm and suicide.
OL,17,F"We will consider the coroner's
OL,18,Ffindings carefully and respond in due
OL,19,Fcourse."
